# UI Design Protection

- Do not modify existing UI design, layout, visual style, spacing, colors, or interaction patterns unless explicitly requested by the user in the current chat.
- UI work is additive only: new features should be added without changing current UI behavior or appearance.
- If a requested feature seems to require UI changes, propose a non-breaking additive approach first.
- Ask for explicit confirmation before any UI refactor, replacement, or removal.
